   <td valign=\"top\" width=\"111\" style=\"padding: 0cm; margin: 0px; border-color: rgb(232, 232, 232); background-color: transparent; width: 83.25pt; height: 33.45pt; \">\r\n                        <p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: left; \"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; \"><font style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: Verdana; \"><font style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-size: 11px; \"><font style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; \"><font style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; \">关键违反-S</font></font><o:p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; \"></o:p></font></font></span></p>\r\n                        </td>\r\n                        <td valign=\"top\" width=\"200\" style=\"padding: 0cm; margin: 0px; border-color: rgb(232, 232, 232); background-color: transparent; width: 150pt; height: 33.45pt; \">\r\n                        <p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: left; \"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10pt; \"><font style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: Verdana; \"><font style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-size: 11px; \">&nbsp;<b style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-size: 11px; \"><font style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; \"><font style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; \">...没有... YES部分：</font></font><o:p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; \"></o:p></b></font></font></span></p>\r\n                        </td>\r\n                    </tr>\r\n                </tbody>\r\n            </table>\r\n            <p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; \">&nbsp;</p>\r\n            <p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: left; \"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; \"><o:p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; \"><font style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: Verdana; font-size: 11px; \">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></p>\r\n            <p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: left; \"><b style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; \"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; \"><font style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: Verdana; \"><font style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-size: 11px; \"><font style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; \"><font style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; \">纠正行动计划</font></font><o:p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; \"></o:p></font></font></span></b></p>\r\n            <p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: left; \"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; \"><font style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: Verdana; \"><font style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-size: 11px; \"><font style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; \"><font style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; \">该纠正行动计划的关键侵犯（D在完成审核问卷调查）及不合格（评分C）。这些研究结果是有效的网站/审计所涵盖的日期-S和数量有限的采访文件检查所施加的时间限制，以及工厂提供的数据和信息的准确性。</font></font><o:p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; \"></o:p></font></font></span></p>\r\n            <p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: left; \"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; \"><o:p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; \"><font style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: Verdana; font-size: 11px; \">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></p>\r\n            <p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: left; \"><font style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: Verdana; \"><font style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-size: 11px; \"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-size: 11px; \"><font style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; \"><font style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; \">纠正行动计划的基础上签署的工厂管理代表及主任审核员在审核末次会议上与工厂management.It应在当地语言发行，副本给工厂representative.If工厂的管理不能承诺立即采取纠正措施和/或目标日期，调用的原因应该指出的核数师根据</font></font></span><span lang=\"ZH-TW\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-size: 11px; \"><font style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; \"><font style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; \">&ldquo;&nbsp;</font></font></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-size: 11px; \"><font style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; \"><font style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; \">工厂代表</font></font></span><span lang=\"ZH-TW\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-size: 11px; \"><font style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; \"><font style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; \">&ldquo; 。</font></font></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-size: 11px; \"><font style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; \"><font style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; \">正式签署的纠正行动计划在当地语言以及打字，英语翻译被发送到本金连同其他申报文件。</font></font><o:p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; \"></o:p></span></font></font></p>\r\n            <p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: left; \"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; \"><o:p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; \"><font style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: Verdana; font-size: 11px; \">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></p>\r\n            <p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: left; \"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; \"><font style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: Verdana; \"><font style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-size: 11px; \"><font style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; \"><font style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; \">本次审计的主要下令一定会重新考虑报告的结论和纠正措施，并追求实现直接与工厂，为适当。</font><font style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; \">主要的可以返回纠正行动计划，与他的确认/适当的评论。</font><font style=\"padding: 0px; 