l or local Labor Code?</td>\r\n                        <td width=\"194\" colspan=\"2\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; \">　</td>\r\n                        <td colspan=\"4\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; \">　</td>\r\n                    </tr>\r\n                    <tr height=\"67\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; \">\r\n                        <td height=\"67\" x:num=\"\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; \"><strong style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; \">6.3</strong></td>\r\n                        <td width=\"257\" colspan=\"2\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; \">Is the factory regularly audited(social audits) by customers or by local labor bureau ? (If yes give details).</td>\r\n                        <td width=\"194\" colspan=\"2\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; \">　</td>\r\n                        <td colspan=\"4\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; \">　</td>\r\n                    </tr>\r\n                </tbody>\r\n            </table>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>','                        社会责任符合性审核清单（三）                                                                   ','社会责任符合性审核清单(三)',72,'','shirui','shirui',1345536916,1345536891,3,0,'auth69.html'),(70,146,'1','社会责任审核符合性清单(一)','','&nbsp;\r\n<table id=\"table7\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"4\" cellpadding=\"8\" width=\"100%\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(35, 90, 128); font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 23px; \">\r\n    <tbody style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; \">\r\n        <tr style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; \">\r\n            <td class=\"wzbt\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; \">社会责任审核符合性清单（一）</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; \">\r\n            <td class=\"nycss\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; \">\r\n            <p style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; \">&nbsp;</p>\r\n            <table border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" width=\"603\" x