ght=\"120\" /></a></td>\r\n            <td><a href=\"http://www.arcandor.com/\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" alt=\"Arcandor\" src=\"http://www.sa8000cn.cn/Article/BSCI/200908/bsci/arcandor.gif\" width=\"120\" height=\"120\" /></a></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><a href=\"http://www.damai.nl/\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" alt=\"Arli Group BV\" src=\"http://www.sa8000cn.cn/Article/BSCI/200908/bsci/029e26268ab419e01ffaadbefaf4760e03ff026c7bf3.gif\" width=\"120\" height=\"120\" /></a></td>\r\n            <td><a href=\"http://www.asmo-id.com/\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" alt=\"Asmo ID\" src=\"http://www.sa8000cn.cn/Article/BSCI/200908/bsci/e19e3a79f801a207c0760f4b4cc7615cf2ff69169466.gif\" width=\"120\" height=\"120\" /></a></td>\r\n            <td><img border=\"0\" alt=\"Aspiria ApS\" src=\"http://www.sa8000cn.cn/Article/BSCI/200908/bsci/8bde027093f17452e9d5e93cad6800d0bd84bd065cde.gif\" width=\"120\" height=\"120\" /></td>\r\n            <td><a href=\"http://www.aswatson.com/\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" alt=\"ASWatson\" src=\"http://www.sa8000cn.cn/Article/BSCI/200908/bsci/mi_aswatson2.gif\" width=\"120\" height=\"120\" /></a></td>\r\n            <td><a href=\"http://www.auluna.com/\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" alt=\"Auluna\" src=\"http://www.sa8000cn.cn/Article/BSCI/200908/bsci/mi_auluna.gif\" width=\"120\" height=\"120\" /></a></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><a href=\"http://www.bintg.com/\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" alt=\"B.I.G. Hermosa Floorcoverings B.V.\" src=\"http://www.sa8000cn.cn/Article/BSCI/200908/bsci/5f3babea2a0bd67fef42dae0e602170a1652ea0f9726.gif\" width=\"120\" height=\"120\" /></a></td>\r\n            <td><img border=\"0\" alt=\"Balancia-Midania\" src=\"http://www.sa8000cn.cn/Article/BSCI/200908/bsci/mi_balancia.gif\" width=\"120\" height=\"120\" /></td>\r\n            <td><a href=\"http://www.baumhueter-international.de/\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" alt=\"Baumh&uuml;ter\" src=\"http://www.sa8000cn.cn/Article/BSCI/200908/bsci/mi_baumhueter.gif\" width=\"120\" height=\"120\" /></a></td>\r\n            <td><a href=\"http://www.bc-europeanstyle.com/\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" alt=\"BCEurope - Cotton\" src=\"http://www.sa8000cn.cn/Article/BSCI/200908/bsci/cotton.gif\" width=\"120\" height=\"120\" /></a></td>\r\n            <td><a href=\"http://www.beldona.ch/\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" alt=\"Beldona\" src=\"http://www.sa8000cn.cn/Article/BSCI/200908/bsci/bd896143c767b5e2463876d102bbe65e938b4582742e.gif\" width=\"120\" height=\"120\" /></a></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><a href=\"http://www.belltex.be/\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" alt=\"Belltex NV\" src=\"http://www.sa8000cn.cn/Article/BSCI/200908/bsci/a588c5eda20a8ad34a6e6abcda36bd4fa144d0b51fa3.gif\" width=\"120\" height=\"120\" /></a></td>\r\n            <td><img border=\"0\" alt=\"Berendsen\" src=\"http://www.sa8000cn.cn/Article/BSCI/200908/bsci/mi_berendsen.gif\" width=\"120\" height=\"120\" /></td>\r\n            <td><a href=\"http://www.bertelstextil.de/\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" alt=\"Bertels Textilhandels\" src=\"http://www.sa8000cn.cn/Article/BSCI/200908/bsci/c5e464f008970800e40a762b22485e24c035ddf771e7.gif\" width=\"120\" height=\"120\" /></a></td>\r\n            <td><a href=\"http://www.beurer.com/\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" alt=\"Beurer GmbH\" src=\"http://www.sa8000cn.cn/Article/BSCI/200908/bsci/BeurerGmbH4d570666afae.gif\" width=\"120\" height=\"120\" /></a></td>\r\n            <td><a href=\"http://www.bierbaum.de/\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" alt=\"Bierbaum Wohnen GmbH &amp; Co. KG (DE)\" src=\"http://www.sa8000cn.cn/Article/BSCI/200908/bsci/mi_bierbaum.gif\" width=\"120\" height=\"120\" /></a></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</center>','BSCI最新成员列表                                                                                                       ','BSCI最新成员列表',502,'','shirui','shirui',1348294243,1348294086,3,0,'factory281.html'),(282,139,'','BSCI验厂让供应商受益','','<div style=\"padding-bottom: 10px; padding-left: 10px; padding-right: 10px; padding-top: 10px\" id=\"ctl00_ContentPlaceHolder1_divContent\">\r\n<div style=\"line-height: 150%; margin: 0pt\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 9pt\"><strong>BSCI验厂让供应商受益</strong></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"line-height: 150%; margin: 0pt\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 9pt\">近年来，可能在大部分供应商的生产</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 9pt\">工厂</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 9pt\">里都接受过各种各样的社会责任审核。各供应商可能会心存疑虑，&ldquo;为什么要再进行另一次社会责任审核？我们为什么需要使用其它新的程序？社会责任审核如何使我们受益？&rdquo;</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"line-height: 12pt; margin: 0pt\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"line-height: 150%; margin: 0pt\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 9pt\">相关的问题并非是供应商引进社会责任标准与否，而是在于：供应商如何确保持续符合社会责任标准并同时从中获益？</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"line-height: 12pt; margin: 0pt\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"line-height: 150%; margin: 0pt\">BSCI监督系统的开发是用来减轻供应商的审核负担。这也是一个联合的过程，也就是说，参与了BSCI的各个行业的公司无需针对形形色色的标准来进行多次审核。这不但为受审核公司节约了费用，同时也节约了时间，否则会让冗长和反反复复的审核耗费大量的时间和金钱。因此不论受审核公司位于哪个国家，其审核要求都是相同的，而其审核结果都会被所有的BSCI成员行业里的各大公司所认可、接受。</div>\r\n<div style=\"line-height: 12pt; margin: 0pt\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"line-height: 150%; margin: 0pt\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 9pt\">而且，一家公司的社会责任表现与其员工的生产力之间存在一种相互关系。不良的社会责任表现会降低员工的生产能力，从而会损及到公司的利益。</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"line-height: 6pt; text-indent: -21.25pt; margin: 0pt 0pt 0pt 21.25pt\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"line-height: 150%; margin: 0pt\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 9pt\">零售公司的协助和联合</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 9pt\">BSCI</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 9pt\">的专家服务者的目标是要实现对供应商社会责任表现进行可持续性的改进和实施。</span></div>\r\n</div>','BSCI验厂让供应商受益近年来，可能在大部分供应商的生产工厂里都接受过各种各样的社会责任审核。各供应商可能会心存疑虑，为什么','BSCI验厂让供应商受益',60,'','shirui','shirui',1348294352,1348294244,3,0,'factory282.html'),(283,139,'','BSCI验厂手册目标和应用范围','','<div style=\"padding-bottom: 10px; padding-left: 10px; padding-right: 10px; padding-top: 10px\" id=\"ctl00_ContentPlaceHolder1_divContent\">\r\n<div><strong>BSCI验厂手册目标和应用范围</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"line-height: 12pt; margin: 0pt\">&nbsp;<span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 9pt\">本手册的制定是用来帮助供应商，同时还有零售商、审核公司以及其它相关方，确保他们在各自责任领域内满足最基本的社会责任、环境标准的要求。关于对供应商公司的期望、他们所要履行的要求以及在整个实施过程中所必须要承担的责任，本手册中提供了明确的信息和实用的解决方案。同时其中还包含了有关如何从必要的变化中获取其它经济方面利益的建议，以及当出现问题时，该如何寻求帮助和支持。</span></div>\r\n<span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 9pt\">\r\n<div style=\"line-height: 12pt; margin: auto 0pt\"><b><font size=\"4\"><span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt\">1.3.1</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt\">.</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt\">参与者及其责任</span></font></b></div>\r\n<div style=\"line-height: 12pt; margin: 14pt 0pt 14.5pt\"><b><font size=\"3\"><span><span><span><span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt\">1.3.1<span style=\"font-size: 9pt\">.1.</span></span></span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt\">供应商</span></font></b></div>\r\n<div style=\"line-height: 150%; margin: 0pt\">BSCI成员的各行业公司决定哪些供应商会包括在BSCI的监督系统中。为了能够在进口市场中最优化地实施这个标准行动，所有的供应商在该行动中联合起来。各行业公司负责决定各供应商的分包商是直接包括在行动之中，还是通过供应商的监督和监控系统间接包括在内。供应商的资料，包括名称、地址以及其它信息都要保存在一个数据库中，该数据库由BSCI的秘书处来管理。</div>\r\n<div style=\"line-height: 12pt; margin: 14pt 0pt 14.5pt\"><b><font size=\"3\"><span><span><span><span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt\">1.3.1</span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt\">.2.</span></span></span></span></span><span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt\">审核公司</span></span></font></b></div>\r\n<div style=\"line-height: 150%; margin: 12pt 0pt 0pt\"><span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 9pt\">执行</span></span><span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 9pt\">BSCI</span></span><span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 9pt\">的审核的审核员的素质和专业技能直接影响到服务的价值，</span></span><span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 9pt\">而且也是</span></span><span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 9pt\">BSCI</span></span><span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 9pt\">系统本身完整的一部分。为了确保审核员的专业技术知识，各审核活动只能由</span></span><span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 9pt\">SAAS</span></span><span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 9pt\">（<i>社会责任认可服务机构</i>）认可的审核公司和审核员执行，在这一点</span></span><span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 9pt\">SAAS</span></span><span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 9pt\">和</span></span><span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 9pt\">BSCI</span></span><span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 9pt\">之间已经达成共识。</span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"line-height: 6pt; margin: 0pt\"><span>&nbsp;</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"line-height: 150%; margin: 0pt\"><span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 9pt\">SAAS</span></span><span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 9pt\">认可的审核公司聘用的审核员必须具备高素质，并且要随时不停的接受培训、进一步的深造及</span></span><span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 9pt\">SAI</span></span><span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 9pt\">的鉴定合格。同时他们也必须：</span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"line-height: 6pt; margin: 0pt\"><span>&nbsp;</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: -14.15pt; margin: 0pt 0pt 0pt 28.35pt\"><span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 9pt\"><span>&middot;<span style=\"font: 7pt \'Times New Roman\'\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 9pt\">绝对是不偏不倚、公平、廉洁。</span></span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: -14.15pt; margin: 0pt 0pt 0pt 28.35pt\"><span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 9pt\"><span>&middot;<span style=\"font: 7pt \'Times New Roman\'\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 9pt\">定期进行验厂。</span></span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: -14.15pt; margin: 0pt 0pt 0pt 28.35pt\"><span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 9pt\"><span>&middot;<span style=\"font: 7pt \'Times New Roman\'\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 9pt\">在相关领域具备丰富的专业经验，比如社会责任审核、车间安全以及质量控制等等。</span></span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: -14.15pt; margin: 0pt 0pt 0pt 28.35pt\"><span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 9pt\"><span>&middot;<span style=\"font: 7pt \'Times New Roman\'\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 9pt\">掌握当地的商业情况，通晓该国语言，并且熟悉当地的文化和思想情况。在一个审核小组中，至少要有一名小组成员必须通晓本地语言并且熟悉当地文化背景。</span></span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: -14.15pt; margin: 0pt 0pt 0pt 28.35pt\"><span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 9pt\"><span>&middot;<span style=\"font: 7pt \'Times New Roman\'\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 9pt\">具备良好的心理素质，交流和人际关系技巧。</span></span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: -14.15pt; margin: 0pt 0pt 0pt 28.35pt\"><span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 9pt\"><span>&middot;<span style=\"font: 7pt \'Times New Roman\'\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 9pt\">愿意接受定期的检查</span></span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: -14.15pt; margin: 0pt 0pt 0pt 28.35pt\"><span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 9pt\"><span>&middot;<span style=\"font: 7pt \'Times New Roman\'\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 9pt\">英文流利，说、写能力强。在一个审核小组中，至少要有一名小组成员必须精通英语。</span></span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: -14.15pt; margin: 0pt 0pt 0pt 28.35pt\"><span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 9pt\"><span>&middot;<span style=\"font: 7pt \'Times New Roman\'\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 9pt\">持有</span></span></span><span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 9pt\">SA8000</span></span><span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 9pt\">审核许可证。在一个审核小组中，至少要有一名小组成员必须拥有审核员资格证书。</span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"line-height: 12pt; margin: 0pt\"><span>&nbsp;</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"line-height: 150%; margin: 0pt\"><span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 9pt\">以上当中没有列明的对审核员的其它要求请参照</span></span><span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 9pt\">SAAS</span></span><span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 9pt\">指南。</span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"line-height: 6pt; margin: 0pt\"><span>&nbsp;</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"line-height: 150%; margin: 0pt\"><span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 9pt\">代表</span></span><span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 9pt\">BSCI</span></span><span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 9pt\">工作的审核公司必须不但要符合</span></span><span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 9pt\">SAAS</span></span><span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 9pt\">要求，同时他们也必须满足以下标准：</span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: -14.15pt; margin: 0pt 0pt 0pt 28.35pt\"><span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 9pt\"><span>&middot;<span style=\"font: 7pt \'Times New Roman\'\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 9pt\">对受审核市场或者国家具有相关经验。</span></span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: -14.15pt; margin: 0pt 0pt 0pt 28.35pt\"><span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 9pt\"><span>&middot;<span style=\"font: 7pt \'Times New Roman\'\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 9pt\">在社会管理系统领域具备丰富经验，同时拥有良好的声誉。</span></span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: -14.15pt; margin: 0pt 0pt 0pt 28.35pt\"><span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 9pt\"><span>&middot;<span style=\"font: 7pt \'Times New Roman\'\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 9pt\">熟知</span></span></span><span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 9pt\">BSCI</span></span><span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 9pt\">系统中的专业知识，这是参与</span></span><span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 9pt\">BSCI</span></span><span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 9pt\">研讨会所需要的要求。</span></span><span>&nbsp;</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"line-height: 12pt; margin: 14pt 0pt 14.5pt\"><b><font size=\"3\"><span><span><span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt\">1.3.1</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt\">.3.</span></span></span></span><span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt\">指导与培训</span></span></font></b></div>\r\n<div style=\"line-height: 6pt; margin: 0pt\"><span>&nbsp;</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"line-height: 150%; margin: 0pt\"><span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 9pt\">BSCI</span></span><span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 9pt\">是一个自发的发展行动。供应商在实施必要的纠正行动过程中会得到</span></span><span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 9pt\">BSCI</span></span><span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 9pt\">成员行业公司的支持。这种合作关系突出了</span></span><span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 9pt\">BSCI</span></span><span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 9pt\">系统的积极作用。</span></span><span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 9pt\">BSCI</span></span><span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 9pt\">不会参与实际的指导工作，也不会在没有跟进的情况下实施社会责任审核。每次审核只能体现某个阶段内，某生产</span></span><span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 9pt\">工厂的</span></span><span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 9pt\">社会责任表现。</span></span><span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 9pt\">BSCI</span></span><span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 9pt\">的目标是要提供一个系统来帮助供应商实现可持续的高水平的社会责任表现。所以，只有当供应商愿意并在审核过程中协助制定自我评估计划和完成其他预先取得相应资格的措施的情况下，这个目标才能实现。这些措施可能包括快速审查、指导和培训。然后，对每次审核中发现的问题而做的纠正行动进行彻底跟进是非常有帮助的。假如供应商某个地方需要帮助，</span></span><span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 9pt\">BSCI</span></span><span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 9pt\">就会确保他们会得到相关领域具备相应资格的专业人员的协助。经验表明，通过每次审核后，供应商的专业准备和资格认定的表现都有很大程度上改善。这就是该个标准行动的目标：通过零售商和专家服务者的有效协助，积极的提高社会标准。</span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"line-height: 6pt; margin: 0pt\"><span>&nbsp;</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"line-height: 150%; margin: 0pt\"><span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 9pt\">向供应商提供的跟进支持包括，对纠正行动计划（</span></span><span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 9pt\">CAP</span></span><span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 9pt\">）的控制，进一步的培训直到包括综合培训和帮助。参与</span></span><span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 9pt\">BSCI</span></span><span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 9pt\">行业的公司决定所要求支持的强度。这会因各具体情况不同而有所不同，这要根据偏离要求的程度，以及在每个情况下，所需要的个别纠正行动的复杂性来决定。</span></span><span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 9pt\">BSCI</span></span><span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 9pt\">各行业公司的员工、服务提供者或者其它具有相关专业技术的组织都可以提供帮助。</span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"line-height: 12pt; margin: 0pt\"><span>&nbsp;</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"line-height: 12pt; margin: 0pt\"><span style=\"font-size: 9pt\">1.3.1</span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt\">.4. </span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt\">BSCI</span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt\">秘书处</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"line-height: 6pt; margin: 0pt\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"line-height: 150%; margin: 0pt\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 9pt\">秘书处的职责包括：</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"line-height: 150%; margin: 0pt\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: -14.15pt; margin: 0pt 0pt 0pt 28.35pt\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 9pt\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7pt \'Times New Roman\'\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 9pt\">全局统筹和项目管理</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: -14.15pt; margin: 0pt 0pt 0pt 28.35pt\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 9pt\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7pt \'Times New Roman\'\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 9pt\">统一的程序和文件的完善</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: -14.15pt; margin: 0pt 0pt 0pt 28.35pt\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 9pt\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7pt \'Times New Roman\'\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 9pt\">程序和文件的实施</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: -14.15pt; margin: 0pt 0pt 0pt 28.35pt\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 9pt\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7pt \'Times New Roman\'\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 9pt\">协调工作：协调所有政治、商业以及利益相关的组织之间的关系</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: -14.15pt; margin: 0pt 0pt 0pt 28.35pt\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 9pt\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7pt \'Times New Roman\'\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 9pt\">公共关系和沟通</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: -14.15pt; margin: 0pt 0pt 0pt 28.35pt\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 9pt\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7pt \'Times New Roman\'\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 9pt\">召集并组织</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 9pt\">BSCI</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 9pt\">成员董事会会议</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"line-height: 12pt; margin: 0pt 0pt 0pt 14.2pt\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"line-height: 12pt; margin: 14pt 0pt 14.5pt\"><b><font size=\"3\"><span><span><span><span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt\">1.3.1</span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt\">.5.</span></span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt\">贸易公司</span></font></b></div>\r\n<div style=\"line-height: 6pt; margin: 0pt\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"line-height: 150%; margin: 0pt\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 9pt\">BSCI</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 9pt\">向欧洲以及国际上的贸易公司和协会开放。</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"line-height: 150%; margin: 0pt\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"line-height: 150%; margin: 0pt\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 9pt\">参与的各贸易公司必须遵守有关</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 9pt\">BSCI</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 9pt\">组织结构的程序、文件以及社会责任的实施。</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"line-height: 150%; margin: 0pt\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"line-height: 150%; margin: 0pt\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 9pt\">参与的每个贸易公司都有一名协调代表公司出席</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 9pt\">BSCI</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 9pt\">成员董事会会议。该协调代表的作用在于调解本公司和其它</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 9pt\">BSCI</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 9pt\">成员或参与方之间的利益。协调代表负责完成</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 9pt\">BSCI</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 9pt\">结构里的成员贸易公司所要完成的任务。这给协调代表带来某些责任，至少包括：</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: -14.15pt; margin: 0pt 0pt 0pt 28.35pt\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 9pt\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7pt \'Times New Roman\'\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 9pt\">在本公司里管理并负责有关</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 9pt\">BSCI</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 9pt\">的事务，并且也是公司与</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 9pt\">BSCI</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 9pt\">秘书处以及其它利益相关方的联系人。</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"line-height: 12pt; text-indent: -14.15pt; margin: 0pt 0pt 0pt 28.35pt\"><span style=\"font-size: 9pt\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7pt \'Times New Roman\'\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt\">就有关</span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt\">BSCI</span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt\">问题对内部（和外部）的沟通。</span></div>\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 9pt\">\r\n<div style=\"line-height: 12pt; margin: 14pt 0pt 14.5pt\"><b><font size=\"3\"><span style=\"font-size: 9pt\">1.3.2</span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt\">.</span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt\">责任概述</span></font></b></div>\r\n<div style=\"line-height: 12pt; margin: 14pt 0pt 14.5pt\"><b><font size=\"3\"><span style=\"font-size: 9pt\">\r\n<table style=\"width: 506.85pt; border-collapse: collapse\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" width=\"676\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"height: 17.65pt\">\r\n            <td style=\"border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; border-left: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-bottom: 2.25pt; padding-left: 2.85pt; width: 44.45pt; padding-right: 2.85pt; background: silver; height: 17.65pt; border-top: windowtext 1pt solid; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-top: 2.25pt\" valign=\"top\" width=\"59\">\r\n            <div style=\"line-height: 11pt; margin: 0pt\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 8pt\">序号</span></b></div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-bottom: 2.25pt; padding-left: 2.85pt; width: 65.8pt; padding-right: 2.85pt; background: silver; height: 17.65pt; border-left-color: #d4d0c8; border-top: windowtext 1pt solid; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-top: 2.25pt\" valign=\"top\" width=\"88\">\r\n            <div style=\"line-height: 11pt; margin: 0pt\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 8pt\">程序</span></b></div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-bottom: 2.25pt; padding-left: 2.85pt; width: 138.55pt; padding-right: 2.85pt; background: silver; height: 17.65pt; border-left-color: #d4d0c8; border-top: windowtext 1pt solid; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-top: 2.25pt\" valign=\"top\" width=\"185\">\r\n            <div style=\"line-height: 11pt; margin: 0pt\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 8pt\">供应商的任务</span></b></div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-bottom: 2.25pt; padding-left: 2.85pt; width: 95.5pt; padding-right: 2.85pt; background: silver; height: 17.65pt; border-left-color: #d4d0c8; border-top: windowtext 1pt solid; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-top: 2.25pt\" valign=\"top\" width=\"127\">\r\n            <div style=\"line-height: 11pt; margin: 0pt\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 8pt\">审核员的任务</span></b></div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-bottom: 2.25pt; padding-left: 2.85pt; width: 162.55pt; padding-right: 2.85pt; background: silver; height: 17.65pt; border-left-color: #d4d0c8; border-top: windowtext 1pt solid; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-top: 2.25pt\" valign=\"top\" width=\"217\">\r\n            <div style=\"line-height: 11pt; margin: 0pt\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 8pt\">参与的贸易公司的任务</span></b></div>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr style=\"height: 42.25pt\">\r\n            <td style=\"border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; border-left: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-bottom: 2.85pt; background-color: transparent; border-top-color: #d4d0c8; padding-left: 2.85pt; width: 44.45pt; padding-right: 2.85pt; height: 42.25pt; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-top: 2.85pt\" valign=\"top\" width=\"59\">\r\n            <div style=\"line-height: 11pt; margin: 0pt\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 8pt\">1.</span></b></div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-bottom: 2.85pt; background-color: transparent; border-top-color: #d4d0c8; padding-left: 2.85pt; width: 65.8pt; padding-right: 2.85pt; height: 42.25pt; border-left-color: #d4d0c8; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-top: 2.85pt\" valign=\"top\" width=\"88\">\r\n            <div style=\"line-height: 11pt; margin: 0pt\"><span style=\"font-size: 8pt\">意识提升阶段</span></div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-bottom: 2.85pt; background-color: transparent; border-top-color: #d4d0c8; padding-left: 2.85pt; width: 138.55pt; padding-right: 2.85pt; height: 42.25pt; border-left-color: #d4d0c8; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-top: 2.85pt\" valign=\"top\" width=\"185\">\r\n            <div style=\"line-height: 11pt; margin: 0pt\"><span style=\"font-size: 8pt\">参与</span><span style=\"font-size: 8pt\">BSCI</span><span style=\"font-size: 8pt\">的基本意识研讨会</span></div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-bottom: 2.85pt; background-color: transparent; border-top-color: #d4d0c8; padding-left: 2.85pt; width: 95.5pt; padding-right: 2.85pt; height: 42.25pt; border-left-color: #d4d0c8; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-top: 2.85pt\" valign=\"top\" width=\"127\">\r\n            <div style=\"line-height: 11pt; margin: 0pt\"><span style=\"font-size: 8pt\">无</span></div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-bottom: 2.85pt; background-color: transparent; border-top-color: #d4d0c8; padding-left: 2.85pt; width: 162.55pt; padding-right: 2.85pt; height: 42.25pt; border-left-color: #d4d0c8; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-top: 2.85pt\" valign=\"top\" width=\"217\">\r\n            <div style=\"line-height: 11pt; margin: 0pt\"><span style=\"font-size: 8pt\">向供应商发出信函，邀请他们加入</span><span style=\"font-size: 8pt\">BSCI</span><span style=\"font-size: 8pt\">基本意识研讨会</span></div>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr style=\"height: 42.25pt\">\r\n            <td style=\"border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; border-left: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-bottom: 2.85pt; background-color: transparent; border-top-color: #d4d0c8; padding-left: 2.85pt; width: 44.45pt; padding-right: 2.85pt; height: 42.25pt; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-top: 2.85pt\" valign=\"top\" width=\"59\">\r\n            <div style=\"line-height: 11pt; margin: 0pt\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 8pt\">2.</span></b></div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-bottom: 2.85pt; background-color: transparent; border-top-color: #d4d0c8; padding-left: 2.85pt; width: 65.8pt; padding-right: 2.85pt; height: 42.25pt; border-left-color: #d4d0c8; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-top: 2.85pt\" valign=\"top\" width=\"88\">\r\n            <div style=\"line-height: 11pt; margin: 0pt\"><span style=\"font-size: 8pt\">准备</span></div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-bottom: 2.85pt; background-color: transparent; border-top-color: #d4d0c8; padding-left: 2.85pt; width: 138.55pt; padding-right: 2.85pt; height: 42.25pt; border-left-color: #d4d0c8; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-top: 2.85pt\" valign=\"top\" width=\"185\">\r\n            <div style=\"line-height: 11pt; margin: 0pt\"><span style=\"font-size: 8pt\">自我评估，进行资格认定措施的预先准备</span></div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-bottom: 2.85pt; background-color: transparent; border-top-color: #d4d0c8; padding-left: 2.85pt; width: 95.5pt; padding-right: 2.85pt; height: 42.25pt; border-left-color: #d4d0c8; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-top: 2.85pt\" valign=\"top\" width=\"127\">\r\n            <div style=\"line-height: 11pt; margin: 0pt\"><span style=\"font-size: 8pt\">无</span></div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-bottom: 2.85pt; background-color: transparent; border-top-color: #d4d0c8; padding-left: 2.85pt; width: 162.55pt; padding-right: 2.85pt; height: 42.25pt; border-left-color: #d4d0c8; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-top: 2.85pt\" valign=\"top\" width=\"217\">\r\n            <div style=\"line-height: 11pt; margin: 0pt\"><span style=\"font-size: 8pt\">实施或者邀请提供帮助者</span></div>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr style=\"height: 42pt\">\r\n            <td style=\"border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; border-left: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-bottom: 2.85pt; background-color: transparent; border-top-color: #d4d0c8; padding-left: 2.85pt; width: 44.45pt; padding-right: 2.85pt; height: 42pt; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-top: 2.85pt\" valign=\"top\" width=\"59\">\r\n            <div style=\"line-height: 11pt; margin: 0pt\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 8pt\">3.</span></b></div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-bottom: 2.85pt; background-color: transparent; border-top-color: #d4d0c8; padding-left: 2.85pt; width: 65.8pt; padding-right: 2.85pt; height: 42pt; border-left-color: #d4d0c8; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-top: 2.85pt\" valign=\"top\" width=\"88\">\r\n            <div style=\"line-height: 11pt; margin: 0pt\"><span style=\"font-size: 8pt\">初次社会责任审核</span></div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-bottom: 2.85pt; background-color: transparent; border-top-color: #d4d0c8; padding-left: 2.85pt; width: 138.55pt; padding-right: 2.85pt; height: 42pt; border-left-color: #d4d0c8; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-top: 2.85pt\" valign=\"top\" width=\"185\">\r\n            <div style=\"line-height: 150%; margin: 0pt\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 8pt\">下订单让具备</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 8pt\">SAI</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 8pt\">鉴定合格水平的审核公司进行审核，除非该订单由参与</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 8pt\">BSCI</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 8pt\">的零售商下达</span></div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-bottom: 2.85pt; background-color: transparent; border-top-color: #d4d0c8; padding-left: 2.85pt; width: 95.5pt; padding-right: 2.85pt; height: 42pt; border-left-color: #d4d0c8; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-top: 2.85pt\" valign=\"top\" width=\"127\">\r\n            <div style=\"line-height: 11pt; margin: 0pt\"><span style=\"font-size: 8pt\">进行审核</span></div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-bottom: 2.85pt; background-color: transparent; border-top-color: #d4d0c8; padding-left: 2.85pt; width: 162.55pt; padding-right: 2.85pt; height: 42pt; border-left-color: #d4d0c8; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-top: 2.85pt\" valign=\"top\" width=\"217\">\r\n            <div style=\"line-height: 150%; margin: 0pt\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 8pt\">下达订单要求通过</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 8pt\">SAI</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 8pt\">鉴定的审核公司进行审核，或者要求供应商下达审核订单</span></div>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</span></font></b></div>\r\n</span></span>\r\n<table style=\"width: 507.1pt; border-collapse: collapse\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" width=\"676\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"height: 15.1pt\">\r\n            <td style=\"border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; border-left: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-bottom: 2.25pt; padding-left: 2.85pt; width: 44.45pt; padding-right: 2.85pt; background: silver; height: 15.1pt; border-top: windowtext 1pt solid; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-top: 2.25pt\" valign=\"top\" width=\"59\">\r\n            <div style=\"line-height: 150%; margin: 0pt\"><b><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 8pt\">No.</span></b><b><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 8pt\">序号</span></b></div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-bottom: 2.25pt; padding-left: 2.85pt; width: 65.8pt; padding-right: 2.85pt; background: silver; height: 15.1pt; border-left-color: #d4d0c8; border-top: windowtext 1pt solid; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-top: 2.25pt\" valign=\"top\" width=\"88\">\r\n            <div style=\"line-height: 150%; margin: 0pt\"><b><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 8pt\">程序</span></b></div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-bottom: 2.25pt; padding-left: 2.85pt; width: 138.65pt; padding-right: 2.85pt; background: silver; height: 15.1pt; border-left-color: #d4d0c8; border-top: windowtext 1pt solid; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-top: 2.25pt\" valign=\"top\" width=\"185\">\r\n            <div style=\"line-height: 150%; margin: 0pt\"><b><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 8pt\">供应商任践</span></b></div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-bottom: 2.25pt; padding-left: 2.85pt; width: 95.55pt; padding-right: 2.85pt; background: silver; height: 15.1pt; border-left-color: #d4d0c8; border-top: windowtext 1pt solid; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-top: 2.25pt\" valign=\"top\" width=\"127\">\r\n            <div style=\"line-height: 150%; margin: 0pt\"><b><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 8pt\">审核员任践</span></b></div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-bottom: 2.25pt; padding-left: 2.85pt; width: 162.65pt; padding-right: 2.85pt; background: silver; height: 15.1pt; border-left-color: #d4d0c8; border-top: windowtext 1pt solid; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-top: 2.25pt\" valign=\"top\" width=\"217\">\r\n            <div style=\"line-height: 150%; margin: 0pt\"><b><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 8pt\">参与的行业公司任践</span></b></div>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr style=\"height: 37.55pt\">\r\n            <td style=\"border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; border-left: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-bottom: 2.85pt; background-color: transparent; border-top-color: #d4d0c8; padding-left: 2.85pt; width: 44.45pt; padding-right: 2.85pt; height: 37.55pt; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-top: 2.85pt\" valign=\"top\" width=\"59\">\r\n            <div style=\"line-height: 150%; margin: 0pt\"><b><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 8pt\">4.</span></b></div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-bottom: 2.85pt; background-color: transparent; border-top-color: #d4d0c8; padding-left: 2.85pt; width: 65.8pt; padding-right: 2.85pt; height: 37.55pt; border-left-color: #d4d0c8; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-top: 2.85pt\" valign=\"top\" width=\"88\">\r\n            <div style=\"line-height: 150%; margin: 0pt\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 8pt\">社会责任审核报告</span></div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-bottom: 2.85pt; background-color: transparent; border-top-color: #d4d0c8; padding-left: 2.85pt; width: 138.65pt; padding-right: 2.85pt; height: 37.55pt; border-left-color: #d4d0c8; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-top: 2.85pt\" valign=\"top\" width=\"185\">\r\n            <div style=\"line-height: 150%; margin: 0pt\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 8pt\">如果供应商已进行过审核，请将审核报告发送至所有参与</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 8pt\">BSCI</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 8pt\">的贸易公司中需要进行审核的零售商客户。</span></div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-bottom: 2.85pt; background-color: transparent; border-top-color: #d4d0c8; padding-left: 2.85pt; width: 95.55pt; padding-right: 2.85pt; height: 37.55pt; border-left-color: #d4d0c8; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-top: 2.85pt\" valign=\"top\" width=\"127\">\r\n            <div style=\"line-height: 150%; margin: 0pt\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 8pt\">制定社会审核报告并发送给客户（副本发送给供应商</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 8pt\">-</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 8pt\">相关的贸易公司）</span></div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-bottom: 2.85pt; background-color: transparent; border-top-color: #d4d0c8; padding-left: 2.85pt; width: 162.65pt; padding-right: 2.85pt; height: 37.55pt; border-left-color: #d4d0c8; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-top: 2.85pt\" valign=\"top\" width=\"217\">\r\n            <div style=\"line-height: 150%; margin: 0pt\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 8pt\">评估社会责任审核报告</span></div>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr style=\"height: 13.4pt\">\r\n            <td style=\"border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; border-left: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-bottom: 2.85pt; background-color: transparent; border-top-color: #d4d0c8; padding-left: 2.85pt; width: 44.45pt; padding-right: 2.85pt; height: 13.4pt; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-top: 2.85pt\" valign=\"top\" width=\"59\">\r\n            <div style=\"line-height: 150%; margin: 0pt\"><b><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 8pt\">5.</span></b></div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-bottom: 2.85pt; background-color: transparent; border-top-color: #d4d0c8; padding-left: 2.85pt; width: 65.8pt; padding-right: 2.85pt; height: 13.4pt; border-left-color: #d4d0c8; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-top: 2.85pt\" valign=\"top\" width=\"88\">\r\n            <div style=\"line-height: 150%; margin: 0pt\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 8pt\">资格准备</span></div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-bottom: 2.85pt; background-color: transparent; border-top-color: #d4d0c8; padding-left: 2.85pt; width: 138.65pt; padding-right: 2.85pt; height: 13.4pt; border-left-color: #d4d0c8; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-top: 2.85pt\" valign=\"top\" width=\"185\">\r\n            <div style=\"line-height: 150%; margin: 0pt\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 8pt\">实行所有的资格认定准备措施</span></div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-bottom: 2.85pt; background-color: transparent; border-top-color: #d4d0c8; padding-left: 2.85pt; width: 95.55pt; padding-right: 2.85pt; height: 13.4pt; border-left-color: #d4d0c8; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-top: 2.85pt\" valign=\"top\" width=\"127\">\r\n            <div style=\"line-height: 150%; margin: 0pt\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 8pt\">无</span></div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-bottom: 2.85pt; background-color: transparent; border-top-color: #d4d0c8; padding-left: 2.85pt; width: 162.65pt; padding-right: 2.85pt; height: 13.4pt; border-left-color: #d4d0c8; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-top: 2.85pt\" valign=\"top\" width=\"217\">\r\n            <div style=\"line-height: 150%; margin: 0pt\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 8pt\">负责实施、或下达订单提供相关服务者</span></div>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr style=\"height: 36.15pt\">\r\n            <td style=\"border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; border-left: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-bottom: 2.85pt; background-color: transparent; border-top-color: #d4d0c8; padding-left: 2.85pt; width: 44.45pt; padding-right: 2.85pt; height: 36.15pt; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-top: 2.85pt\" valign=\"top\" width=\"59\">\r\n            <div style=\"line-height: 150%; margin: 0pt\"><b><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 8pt\">6.</span></b></div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-bottom: 2.85pt; background-color: transparent; border-top-color: #d4d0c8; padding-left: 2.85pt; width: 65.8pt; padding-right: 2.85pt; height: 36.15pt; border-left-color: #d4d0c8; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-top: 2.85pt\" valign=\"top\" width=\"88\">\r\n            <div style=\"line-height: 150%; margin: 0pt\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 8pt\">纠正行动计划（</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 8pt\">CAP</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 8pt\">）</span></div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-bottom: 2.85pt; background-color: transparent; border-top-color: #d4d0c8; padding-left: 2.85pt; width: 138.65pt; padding-right: 2.85pt; height: 36.15pt; border-left-color: #d4d0c8; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-top: 2.85pt\" valign=\"top\" width=\"185\">\r\n            <div style=\"line-height: 150%; margin: 0pt\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 8pt\">实施纠正行动计划</span></div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-bottom: 2.85pt; background-color: transparent; border-top-color: #d4d0c8; padding-left: 2.85pt; width: 95.55pt; padding-right: 2.85pt; height: 36.15pt; border-left-color: #d4d0c8; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-top: 2.85pt\" valign=\"top\" width=\"127\">\r\n            <div style=\"line-height: 150%; margin: 0pt\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 8pt\">咨询并和供应商在</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 8pt\">CAP</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 8pt\">上达成共识，并制定</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 8pt\">CAP</span></div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-bottom: 2.85pt; background-color: transparent; border-top-color: #d4d0c8; padding-left: 2.85pt; width: 162.65pt; padding-right: 2.85pt; height: 36.15pt; border-left-color: #d4d0c8; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-top: 2.85pt\" valign=\"top\" width=\"217\">\r\n            <div style=\"line-height: 150%; margin: 0pt\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 8pt\">无</span></div>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr style=\"page-break-inside: avoid; height: 37.75pt\">\r\n            <td style=\"border-bottom: black 1pt solid; border-left: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-bottom: 2.85pt; background-color: transparent; border-top-color: #d4d0c8; padding-left: 2.85pt; width: 44.45pt; padding-right: 2.85pt; height: 37.75pt; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-top: 2.85pt\" valign=\"top\" rowspan=\"2\" width=\"59\">\r\n            <div style=\"line-height: 150%; margin: 0pt\"><b><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 8pt\">7.</span></b></div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"border-bottom: black 1pt solid; padding-bottom: 2.85pt; background-color: transparent; border-top-color: #d4d0c8; padding-left: 2.85pt; width: 65.8pt; padding-right: 2.85pt; height: 37.75pt; border-left-color: #d4d0c8; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-top: 2.85pt\" valign=\"top\" rowspan=\"2\" width=\"88\">\r\n            <div style=\"line-height: 150%; margin: 0pt\"><font size=\"2\">社会责任重新审核</font></div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"border-bottom-color: #d4d0c8; padding-bottom: 2.85pt; background-color: transparent; border-top-color: #d4d0c8; padding-left: 2.85pt; width: 138.65pt; padding-right: 2.85pt; height: 37.75pt; border-left-color: #d4d0c8; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-top: 2.85pt\" valign=\"top\" width=\"185\">\r\n            <div style=\"line-height: 150%; margin: 0pt\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 8pt\">下订单让具备</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 8pt\">SAI</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 8pt\">鉴定合格水平的审核公司进行重新审核，除非该订单由参与</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 8pt\">BSCI</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 8pt\">的零售商下达</span></div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"border-bottom-color: #d4d0c8; padding-bottom: 2.85pt; background-color: transparent; border-top-color: #d4d0c8; padding-left: 2.85pt; width: 95.55pt; padding-right: 2.85pt; height: 37.75pt; border-left-color: #d4d0c8; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-top: 2.85pt\" valign=\"top\" rowspan=\"2\" width=\"127\">\r\n            <div style=\"line-height: 150%; margin: 0pt\"><font size=\"3\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 8pt\">进行重新审核</span></font></div>\r\n            <div style=\"line-height: 150%; margin: 0pt\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-bottom: 2.85pt; background-color: transparent; border-top-color: #d4d0c8; padding-left: 2.85pt; width: 162.65pt; padding-right: 2.85pt; height: 37.75pt; border-left-color: #d4d0c8; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-top: 2.85pt\" valign=\"top\" rowspan=\"2\" width=\"217\">\r\n            <div style=\"line-height: 150%; margin: 0pt\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 8pt\">下订单让具备</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 8pt\">SAAS</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 8pt\">鉴定合格水平的审核公司进行重新审核，或者要求供应商下达审核订单，并对重新评估审核报告，如果适用上述第四项目中的规定。</span></div>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr style=\"page-break-inside: avoid; height: 18.6pt\">\r\n            <td style=\"border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-bottom: 2.85pt; background-color: transparent; border-top-color: #d4d0c8; padding-left: 2.85pt; width: 138.65pt; padding-right: 2.85pt; height: 18.6pt; border-left-color: #d4d0c8; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-top: 2.85pt\" valign=\"top\" width=\"185\">\r\n            <div style=\"line-height: 150%; margin: 0pt\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 8pt\">将社会重新审核报告（或者</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 8pt\">SA8000/</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 8pt\">同等证书）的副本发送给各参与的零售商客户</span></div>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr style=\"height: 28.85pt\">\r\n            <td style=\"border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; border-left: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-bottom: 2.85pt; background-color: transparent; border-top-color: #d4d0c8; padding-left: 2.85pt; width: 44.45pt; padding-right: 2.85pt; height: 28.85pt; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-top: 2.85pt\" valign=\"top\" width=\"59\">\r\n            <div style=\"line-height: 150%; margin: 0pt\"><b><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 8pt\">8.</span></b></div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-bottom: 2.85pt; background-color: transparent; border-top-color: #d4d0c8; padding-left: 2.85pt; width: 65.8pt; padding-right: 2.85pt; height: 28.85pt; border-left-color: #d4d0c8; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-top: 2.85pt\" valign=\"top\" width=\"88\">\r\n            <div style=\"line-height: 150%; margin: 0pt\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 8pt\">社会责任重新审核报告</span></div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-bottom: 2.85pt; background-color: transparent; border-top-color: #d4d0c8; padding-left: 2.85pt; width: 138.65pt; padding-right: 2.85pt; height: 28.85pt; border-left-color: #d4d0c8; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-top: 2.85pt\" valign=\"top\" width=\"185\">\r\n            <div style=\"line-height: 150%; margin: 0pt\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 8pt\">如果公司自己已要求并进行过审核，请将社会责任重新审核报告发送至</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 8pt\">BSCI</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 8pt\">行业公司中需要进行重新审核的所有零售客户。</span></div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-bottom: 2.85pt; background-color: transparent; padding-left: 2.85pt; width: 95.55pt; padding-right: 2.85pt; height: 28.85pt; border-left-color: #d4d0c8; border-top: windowtext 1pt solid; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-top: 2.85pt\" valign=\"top\" width=\"127\">\r\n            <div style=\"line-height: 150%; margin: 0pt\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 8pt\">制定社会责任重新审核报告并将它发送给客户（同时把副本发送给供应商</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 8pt\">-</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 8pt\">相关的贸易公司）</span></div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-bottom: 2.85pt; background-color: transparent; border-top-color: #d4d0c8; padding-left: 2.85pt; width: 162.65pt; padding-right: 2.85pt; height: 28.85pt; border-left-color: #d4d0c8; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-top: 2.85pt\" valign=\"top\" width=\"217\">\r\n            <div style=\"line-height: 150%; margin: 0pt\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 8pt\">评估社会责任重新审核报告</span></div>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr style=\"height: 36.15pt\">\r\n            <td style=\"border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; border-left: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-bottom: 2.85pt; background-color: transparent; border-top-color: #d4d0c8; padding-left: 2.85pt; width: 44.45pt; padding-right: 2.85pt; height: 36.15pt; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-top: 2.85pt\" valign=\"top\" width=\"59\">\r\n            <div style=\"line-height: 150%; margin: 0pt\"><b><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 8pt\">9.</span></b></div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-bottom: 2.85pt; background-color: transparent; border-top-color: #d4d0c8; padding-left: 2.85pt; width: 65.8pt; padding-right: 2.85pt; height: 36.15pt; border-left-color: #d4d0c8; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-top: 2.85pt\" valign=\"top\" width=\"88\">\r\n            <div style=\"line-height: 150%; margin: 0pt\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 8pt\">纠正行动计划</span></div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-bottom: 2.85pt; background-color: transparent; border-top-color: #d4d0c8; padding-left: 2.85pt; width: 138.65pt; padding-right: 2.85pt; height: 36.15pt; border-left-color: #d4d0c8; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-top: 2.85pt\" valign=\"top\" width=\"185\">\r\n            <div style=\"line-height: 150%; margin: 0pt\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 8pt\">实施纠正行动计划</span></div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-bottom: 2.85pt; background-color: transparent; border-top-color: #d4d0c8; padding-left: 2.85pt; width: 95.55pt; padding-right: 2.85pt; height: 36.15pt; border-left-color: #d4d0c8; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-top: 2.85pt\" valign=\"top\" width=\"127\">\r\n            <div style=\"line-height: 150%; margin: 0pt\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 8pt\">咨询并和供应商在</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 8pt\">CAP</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 8pt\">（纠正行动计划）上达成共识，并制定</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 8pt\">CAP</span></div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-bottom: 2.85pt; background-color: transparent; border-top-color: #d4d0c8; padding-left: 2.85pt; width: 162.65pt; padding-right: 2.85pt; height: 36.15pt; border-left-color: #d4d0c8; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-top: 2.85pt\" valign=\"top\" width=\"217\">\r\n            <div style=\"line-height: 150%; margin: 0pt\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 8pt\">无</span></div>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr style=\"height: 28.45pt\">\r\n            <td style=\"border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; border-left: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-bottom: 2.85pt; background-color: transparent; border-top-color: #d4d0c8; padding-left: 2.85pt; width: 44.45pt; padding-right: 2.85pt; height: 28.45pt; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-top: 2.85pt\" valign=\"top\" width=\"59\">\r\n            <div style=\"line-height: 150%; margin: 0pt\"><b><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 8pt\">10.</span></b></div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-bottom: 2.85pt; background-color: transparent; border-top-color: #d4d0c8; padding-left: 2.85pt; width: 65.8pt; padding-right: 2.85pt; height: 28.45pt; border-left-color: #d4d0c8; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-top: 2.85pt\" valign=\"top\" width=\"88\">\r\n            <div style=\"line-height: 150%; margin: 0pt\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 8pt\">自初次审核当日起之后三年内需要再次进行审核</span></div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-bottom: 2.85pt; background-color: transparent; border-top-color: #d4d0c8; padding-left: 2.85pt; width: 138.65pt; padding-right: 2.85pt; height: 28.45pt; border-left-color: #d4d0c8; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-top: 2.85pt\" valign=\"top\" width=\"185\">\r\n            <div style=\"line-height: 150%; margin: 0pt\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 8pt\">下订单让具备</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 8pt\">SAI</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 8pt\">鉴定合格水平的审核公司进行审核，除非该订单由参与</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 8pt\">BSCI</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 8pt\">的零售商下达</span></div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-bottom: 2.85pt; background-color: transparent; border-top-color: #d4d0c8; padding-left: 2.85pt; width: 95.55pt; padding-right: 2.85pt; height: 28.45pt; border-left-color: #d4d0c8; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-top: 2.85pt\" valign=\"top\" width=\"127\">\r\n            <div style=\"line-height: 150%; margin: 0pt\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 8pt\">如上所述</span></div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-bottom: 2.85pt; background-color: transparent; border-top-color: #d4d0c8; padding-left: 2.85pt; width: 162.65pt; padding-right: 2.85pt; height: 28.45pt; border-left-color: #d4d0c8; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-top: 2.85pt\" valign=\"top\" width=\"217\">\r\n            <div style=\"line-height: 150%; margin: 0pt\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 8pt\">如上所述</span></div>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>','BSCI验厂手册目标和应用范围本手册的制定是用来帮助供应商，同时还有零售商、审核公司以及其它相关方，确保他们在各自责任领域内','BSCI验厂手册目标和应用范围',95,'','shirui','shirui',1348294497,1348294353,3,0,'factory283.html'),(284,139,'','BSCI验厂基本规章','','<div style=\"padding-bottom: 10px; padding-left: 10px; padding-right: 10px; padding-top: 10px\" id=\"ctl00_ContentPlaceHolder1_divContent\">\r\n<div><strong>BSCI验厂基本规章</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"line-height: 150%; margin: 0pt\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 9pt\">BSCI</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 9pt\">以所有供应商发挥他们的最佳能力来遵守国家和地区的劳工和社会法律、法规以及如下所列国际公约和宣言为基本起点。相关细节参阅</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 9pt\">BSCI</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 9pt\">审核问卷调查表。该问卷调查表会不停的更新；因此使用最新版本这一点很重要。</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"line-height: 12pt; margin: 14pt 0pt 14.5pt\"><b><font size=\"3\"><span style=\"font-size: 9pt\">1.4.1</span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt\">.</span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt\">国家法规要求</span></font></b></div>\r\n<div style=\"line-height: 12pt; margin: 0pt\"><span style=\"font-size: 9pt\">遵守所在国的合法要，特别是关于以下几方面：</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"line-height: 6pt; margin: 0pt\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"line-height: 12pt; text-indent: -14.15pt; margin: 0pt 0pt 0pt 28.35pt\"><span style=\"font-size: 9pt\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7pt \'Times New Roman\'\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt\">商业运作</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"line-height: 12pt; text-indent: -14.15pt; margin: 0pt 0pt 0pt 28.35pt\"><span style=\"font-size: 9pt\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7pt \'Times New Roman\'\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt\">工时</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"line-height: 12pt; text-indent: -14.15pt; margin: 0pt 0pt 0pt 28.35pt\"><span style=\"font-size: 9pt\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7pt \'Times New Roman\'\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt\">薪资和其它报酬</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"line-height: 12pt; text-indent: -14.15pt; margin: 0pt 0pt 0pt 28.35pt\"><span style=\"font-size: 9pt\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7pt \'Times New Roman\'\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt\">社会保险</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"line-height: 12pt; text-indent: -14.15pt; margin: 0pt 0pt 0pt 28.35pt\"><span style=\"font-size: 9pt\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7pt \'Times New Roman\'\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt\">员工的最低年龄限制</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"line-height: 12pt; text-indent: -14.15pt; margin: 0pt 0pt 0pt 28.35pt\"><span style=\"font-size: 9pt\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7pt \'Times New Roman\'\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt\">禁止强迫劳工</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"line-height: 12pt; text-indent: -14.15pt; margin: 0pt 0pt 0pt 28.35pt\"><span style=\"font-size: 9pt\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7pt \'Times New Roman\'\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt\">惩戒性措施</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"line-height: 12pt; text-indent: -14.15pt; margin: 0pt 0pt 0pt 28.35pt\"><span style=\"font-size: 9pt\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7pt \'Times New Roman\'\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt\">结社、集体谈判自由</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"line-height: 12pt; text-indent: -14.15pt; margin: 0pt 0pt 0pt 28.35pt\"><span style=\"font-size: 9pt\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7pt \'Times New Roman\'\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt\">禁止歧视</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"line-height: 12pt; text-indent: -14.15pt; margin: 0pt 0pt 0pt 28.35pt\"><span style=\"font-size: 9pt\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7pt \'Times New Roman\'\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt\">工作条件</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"line-height: 12pt; text-indent: -14.15pt; margin: 0pt 0pt 0pt 28.35pt\"><span style=\"font-size: 9pt\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7pt \'Times New Roman\'\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt\">职业安全与卫生</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"line-height: 12pt; text-indent: -14.15pt; margin: 0pt 0pt 0pt 28.35pt\"><span style=\"font-size: 9pt\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7pt \'Times New Roman\'\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt\">员工住宿方面的法规要求（集体宿舍、住房等等），如涉及；</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"line-height: 12pt; text-indent: -14.15pt; margin: 0pt 0pt 0pt 28.35pt\"><span style=\"font-size: 9pt\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7pt \'Times New Roman\'\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt\">基本的环境要求</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"line-height: 12pt; margin: 0pt\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"line-height: 12pt; margin: 14pt 0pt 14.5pt\"><b><font size=\"3\"><span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt\">1.4.2</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt\">.</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt\">国际法规</span></font></b></div>\r\n<div style=\"line-height: 150%; margin: 0pt\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 9pt\">在</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 9pt\">BSCI</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 9pt\">中的社会标准是以国际劳工组织（</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 9pt\">ILO</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 9pt\">；详见网站</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 9pt\"><a href=\"http://www.ilo.org/\">www.ilo.org</a></span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 9pt\">）中的主要劳工标准为基础。适用于以下工作标准：</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"line-height: 6pt; margin: 0pt\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"line-height: 12pt; text-indent: -14.15pt; margin: 0pt 0pt 0pt 28.35pt\"><span style=\"font-size: 9pt\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7pt \'Times New Roman\'\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt\">国际劳工组织公约</span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt\">第</span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt\">1</span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt\">号</span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt\"> (</span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt\">工作时间</span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt\">)</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"line-height: 12pt; text-indent: -14.15pt; margin: 0pt 0pt 0pt 28.35pt\"><span style=\"font-size: 9pt\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7pt \'Times New Roman\'\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt\">国际劳工组织公约</span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt\">第</span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt\">29</span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt\">号</span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt\">和第</span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt\">1</span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt\">05</span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt\">号</span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt\"> (</span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt\">强迫性劳动和债务工</span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt\">)</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"line-height: 12pt; text-indent: -14.15pt; margin: 0pt 0pt 0pt 28.35pt\"><span style=\"font-size: 9pt\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7pt \'Times New Roman\'\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt\">国际劳工组织公约</span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt\">第</span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt\">79</span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt\">号</span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt\"> (</span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt\">儿童的夜间工作</span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt\">)</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"line-height: 12pt; text-indent: -14.15pt; margin: 0pt 0pt 0pt 28.35pt\"><span style=\"font-size: 9pt\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7pt \'Times New Roman\'\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt\">国际劳工组织公约</span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt\">第</span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt\">87</span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt\">号</span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt\"> (</span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt\">结社自由</span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt\">)</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"line-height: 12pt; text-indent: -14.15pt; margin: 0pt 0pt 0pt 28.35pt\"><span style=\"font-size: 9pt\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7pt \'Times New Roman\'\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt\">国际劳工组织公约</span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt\">第</span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt\">98</span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt\">号</span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt\"> (</span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt\">集体谈判权利</span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt\">)</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"line-height: 12pt; text-indent: -14.15pt; margin: 0pt 0pt 0pt 28.35pt\"><span style=\"font-size: 9pt\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7pt \'Times New Roman\'\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt\">国际劳工组织公约</span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt\">第</span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt\">100</span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt\">号</span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt\">和第</span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt\"> 111 </span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt\">号</span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt\">(</span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt\">男女同工同酬；歧视</span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt\">)</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"line-height: 12pt; text-indent: -14.15pt; margin: 0pt 0pt 0pt 28.35pt\"><span style=\"font-size: 9pt\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7pt \'Times New Roman\'\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt\">国际劳工组织公约</span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt\">第</span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt\">135</span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt\">号</span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt\"> (</span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt\">工人代表</span><sp